{
  "name": "HPageBreaks",
  "summary": "<p>每个水平分页符都由一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/HPageBreak/HPageBreak .htm#HPageBreak.HPageBreak\">HPageBreak</a></strong> 对象代表。</p>\n<p>如果添加的分页符不和打印区域交叠，则新添加的 <strong>HPageBreak</strong> 对象将不会出现在打印区域的 <strong>HPageBreaks</strong> 集合中。如果重新调整打印区域或重新定义打印区域，将会改变集合的内容。</p>\n<p>当 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a></strong> 属性、<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/HPageBreaks/HPageBreaks .htm#HPageBreaks.Count\"><strong>Count</strong></a> 属性、<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/HPageBreaks/HPageBreaks .htm#HPageBreaks.Item\">Item</a></strong> 属性、<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/HPageBreaks/HPageBreaks .htm#HPageBreaks.Parent\">Parent</a></strong> 属性或 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/HPageBreaks/HPageBreaks .htm#HPageBreaks.Add\">Add</a></strong> 方法配合 <strong>HPageBreaks</strong> 属性一起使用时：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>对于自动打印区域，<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/HPageBreaks/HPageBreaks .htm#HPageBreaks.HPageBreaks\">HPageBreaks</a></strong> 属性只应用于打印区域内的分页符。</li>\n<li>对于同一区域中用户定义的打印区域，<strong>HPageBreaks</strong> 属性应用于所有的分页符。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>每张工作表最多有 1026 个水平分页符。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>HPageBreaks</strong> 属性可返回 <strong>HPageBreaks</strong> 集合。使用 <strong>Add</strong> 方法可添加一个水平分页符。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表选中的单元格区域上方添加水平分页符。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveCell</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一个工作表中水平分页符的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> count = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">HPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`水平分页符的数量是 <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${count}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>打印区域内水平分页符的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a></strong> 对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表集合中对象的数量。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一个工作表中水平分页符的数量。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> count = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">HPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`水平分页符的数量是 <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${count}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Add",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>添加水平分页符。返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/HPageBreak/HPageBreak .htm#HPageBreak.HPageBreak\">HPageBreak</a></strong> 对象，它代表新的水平分页符。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一个工作表的单元格 F25 上方添加水平分页符，在其左侧添加垂直分页符*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sheet1 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    sheet1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(sheet1.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;F25&quot;</span>))\n    sheet1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">VPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(sheet1.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;F25&quot;</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在工作表Sheet1中第8行添加一条水平分页符，并显示水平分页符总数。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sheet1 = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>)\n    sheet1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(sheet1.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Rows</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">8</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`水平分页符的数量是 <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${sheet1.HPageBreaks.Count}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Before",
          "type": "Object",
          "description": "<p>一个 Range 对象。新的分页符将添加到该区域上方。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "HPageBreak"
    },
    {
      "name": "Item",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>从集合中返回一个对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例移动第一个工作表的第一个水平分页符至E5单元格*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">HPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Location</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;E5&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一个工作表的第2个水平分页符是否为全屏应用*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> hPageBreak = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">HPageBreaks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(hPageBreak.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Extent</span> == xlPageBreakFull)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "number（int4 精度）",
          "description": "<p>对象的索引号。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "HPageBreak"
    }
  ]
}